data.description: Country living at its finest in beautiful Jasper!! Private "corner" lot on a cul-de-sac, beautifully well maintained home with gleaming hardwoods throughout, large kitchen, highly desired oversized master on main, FIVE total bedrooms, fully finished basement with its own private entrance and capacity to be an in-law suite, two spacious decks overlooking nature, and a short drive from all of the charm that downtown Jasper has to offer. This property is everything you need and won't last long!! Schedule your showing today!!
